  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p> You expel a powerful bullet of acid from your body. Make a ranged ninjutsu attack against a creature within range, dealing 4d8 acid damage on a hit and forcing the target to make a constitution saving throw. On a failed save, the target gains 1 rank of the corroded condition and is blinded until the end of their next turn.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and damage by 2d8. If this jutsu it cast at B-Rank increase the number of creatures you can target by +1.</p>",
